<commentInRDBMS><![CDATA[An Asset pool (subject to a Securitisation and other credit transfer) is a pool of assets that is subject to a Securitisation or other credit transfer. It may comprise Instruments or (parts of) Security positions that have been removed from the Reporting agents' balance sheet, e.g. in case of a Traditional securitisation using an SSPE, where the Reporting agents acts in the role of a Servicer.]]></commentInRDBMS>
